platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: You dont have to be a spatial genius to love this gorgeous puzzlerthough its creator, architecture student Miro Straka, sure is. Hes figured out how to make a game where waging war on rotating cubes is, for all its intricacies, amazingly easy to get into. As bosses, teleporters and other new wrinkles appear, the levels just get that much more fascinatingand incredibly fun to play.
